desc: A piece of Van Nader that closely resembles machinery.

dictionary.lore: The Summoner's Council is still collecting clues as to whether Van Lucy and Van Nader are either real demons, mechanical creations of the gods, or something else entirely. From all of the metal organs that can be obtained from these demons, this organ is the most important. The current samples in the laboratory were collected from various battlegrounds. If a whole body were to be collected, what mysteries could it unfold?

name: Holy Circuit
